room_title: Escape room "The Penitentiary" by OMEscape in New York
room_description:
One of the most infamous rampage killers in American history, Richard Ramirez, AKA “The Night Stalker,” was reported dead of natural causes last year. Rumor says another prisoner found a weird-looking machine in his cell, but he didn't live to tell the tale...
You wake up and find yourselves locked in a cramped cell. Silence and cold stone walls surround you. Suddenly you realize this is the cell the “The Night Stalker” died in! Even if you think it's just a game, you better find a way out of here, and fast.
